Package: huphydown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template for physics students at Humboldt-University of Berlin using the bookdown package
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Jakob", "Napiontek", email = "jakob.napiontek@physik.hu-berlin.de", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Using the bookdown package and templates from HU Berlin Institute of Physics, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots and analyses as well. Based on Chester Ismay's `thesisdown` package.
Maintainer: Jakob Napiontek <jakob.napiontek@physik.hu-berlin.de>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    here
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - https://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
